	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's called the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Konami_code_games" class="postlink">Konami code</a>, and it was purposefully put in the game by the developers, so it's not a glitch.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


