<br />
<br />Same thing to you Nadia, which do you mean, NES Contra or SNES Contra 3?
<br />
<br />If either of you are thinking Konami Code, then I'd know you mean the NES version as the SNES Contra 3 which has codes for Japan doesn't use the Konami Code.
<br />
<br />Nadia what do you mean how can this be achieved? All your Lives are is a variable which has to be set somewhere in code to a specific value which can easily be changed by altering a single byte of ROM.

		

